<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">

  <PropertyGroup>
    <OutputType>Exe</OutputType>
    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>
    <ImplicitUsings>enable</ImplicitUsings>
    <Nullable>enable</Nullable>
    <PackAsTool>true</PackAsTool>
    <ToolCommandName>microkit</ToolCommandName>
    <PackageId>MicroserviceKit</PackageId>
    <Version>0.4.1</Version>
    <Authors>Paweł Pilichowski</Authors>
    <Description>🚀 Complete toolkit for generating production-ready .NET 8 microservices with DDD, CQRS, Clean Architecture, Event-Driven Architecture, and comprehensive infrastructure. Generate enterprise-grade microservices with REST APIs, CQRS, MongoDB read models, RabbitMQ messaging, external service integration, Docker, and complete testing suite.</Description>
    <PackageTags>microservices;toolkit;generator;ddd;cqrs;dotnet;clean-architecture;rest-api;event-driven;mongodb;rabbitmq;docker;enterprise;microkit</PackageTags>
    <PackageLicenseExpression>MIT</PackageLicenseExpression>
    <PackageProjectUrl>https://github.com/suranig/microservice-net8-ddd</PackageProjectUrl>
    <RepositoryUrl>https://github.com/suranig/microservice-net8-ddd</RepositoryUrl>
    <RepositoryType>git</RepositoryType>
    <PackageReadmeFile>README.md</PackageReadmeFile>
    <PackageReleaseNotes>
🎉 Release 0.4.1 - Critical Bug Fixes &amp; Production Stability!

🐛 CRITICAL BUG FIXES:
- 🛠️ Fixed hardcoded entity constructor causing compilation errors - now flexible with developer guidance
- 📁 Fixed fragile template path resolution causing "template not found" in packaged CLI
- 🐳 Fixed Dockerfile path errors and conditional COPY statements for Docker build failures
- 🔧 Fixed incorrect configuration property access in DockerModule

✅ TEMPLATE ENGINE IMPROVEMENTS:
- 🎯 Robust multi-strategy template discovery (env vars, assembly location, directory traversal)
- 📝 Enhanced entity creation with flexible constructor patterns and helpful comments
- 🏗️ Conditional Docker project copying based on architecture level (minimal/standard/enterprise)
- 🚀 Improved error handling and validation feedback throughout generation process

✅ DEVELOPER EXPERIENCE:
- 💡 Generated code now includes helpful comments and customization guidance
- 🔍 Better error messages and validation feedback
- 📋 Standardized file generation patterns across all template modules
- 🎨 Enhanced CLI reliability across different deployment scenarios

🚀 PRODUCTION READY: All critical bugs fixed - reliable template generation and Docker builds guaranteed!
    </PackageReleaseNotes>
  </PropertyGroup>

  <ItemGroup>
    <PackageReference Include="System.CommandLine" Version="2.0.0-beta4.22272.1" />
    <PackageReference Include="Microsoft.Extensions.DependencyInjection" Version="8.0.0" />
    <PackageReference Include="Microsoft.Extensions.Logging" Version="8.0.0" />
    <PackageReference Include="Microsoft.Extensions.Logging.Console" Version="8.0.0" />
  </ItemGroup>

  <ItemGroup>
